Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.55,0:00:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要給度西斯反擊的空檔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.15,0:00:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快準備發射，快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.68,0:00:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,閣下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.25,0:00:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,皇帝陛下駕崩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.89,0:00:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼，真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.72,0:00:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.46,0:00:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和宰相同歸於盡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.93,0:00:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陛下…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.30,0:00:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裝彈完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.40,0:00:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蒸汽壓上升
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.24,0:00:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陛下已經駕崩\N安那托勒只能靠我們來死守了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.94,0:00:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,閣下，是烏爾班號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.15,0:00:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烏爾班號…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.68,0:00:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.63,0:01:08.15,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,just keep on trying, keep on flying\N{\c&HFFBF00&}just keep on trying, keep on flying
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.23,0:01:11.60,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be the light\N{\c&HFFBF00&}I will be the light
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.67,0:01:18.40,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果說把黎明　當作是一個開始\N{\c&HFFBF00&}夜明けをひと　つの始まりとするなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.07,0:01:25.60,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果說現在就是來臨的時刻\N{\c&HFFBF00&}今が来るべき時だとするなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.01,0:01:32.25,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,與你的煙雲時代交響曲 飛向雲海的彼端 \N{\c&HFFBF00&}君とのCloud Age Symphony  雲の海の向こうに
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.32,0:01:40.19,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,飛往光芒照射的方向\N{\c&HFFBF00&}光が射す方へ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.56,0:01:54.84,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah～是否可以遇見有如魔法的那瞬間？\N{\c&HFFBF00&}Ah～魔法のような一瞬に会えるのか？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.91,0:02:09.35,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,取代寒冷的黑夜  我倆展翅飛翔\N{\c&HFFBF00&}冷たい夜を引き替えに  二人は羽ばたいて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.42,0:02:18.80,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,在那盡頭  抓住了永恆…\N{\c&HFFBF00&}永远を掴む、その果てには
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.52,0:02:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H8dccf0&}備齊材料\NMaking material
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.87,0:02:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,潘朵拉巨砲\N似乎已經進入發射準備狀態了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.84,0:02:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,槍砲長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.14,0:02:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魚雷瞄準定位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.74,0:03:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目標，潘朵拉巨砲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.58,0:03:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一號二號裝彈完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.08,0:03:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發射準備就緒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.48,0:03:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,信號彈，發射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.48,0:03:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烏爾班發出了信號彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.58,0:03:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以公主殿下之名\N命全軍立刻停止作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.02,0:03:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下好像在烏爾班號上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.59,0:03:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經自認是皇帝了是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.86,0:03:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她父王明明才剛駕崩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.36,0:03:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是大不敬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.27,0:03:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別管她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.23,0:03:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把烏爾班號\N和度西斯艦隊一起轟掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.37,0:03:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是這樣公主殿下會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.77,0:03:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係，發射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.37,0:03:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.41,0:03:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘇菲亞殿下，就請您為\N安那托勒的重生而犧牲吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.55,0:03:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六號準備就緒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.05,0:03:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七號準備就緒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.38,0:03:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八號準備就緒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.25,0:03:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,潘朵拉巨砲\N正持續進行發射準備中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.76,0:03:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.16,0:03:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發射魚雷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.37,0:04:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,潘朵拉巨砲確定已爆炸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.37,0:04:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,度西斯艦隊後方\N有其他艦隊正在接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.61,0:04:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來的真是時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.62,0:04:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這停戰命令…到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.65,0:04:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,司令，後方有艦隊接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.66,0:04:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快去確認對方身分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.90,0:04:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼時候\N和麥德賽侯爵達成串連的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.73,0:04:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這人的好處就是應變得很快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.73,0:04:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是麥德賽艦隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.17,0:04:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前仍在接近中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.57,0:04:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,司令，這是陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.41,0:04:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一來停戰命令\N根本就失去了意義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.01,0:04:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備迎擊敵方砲火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.75,0:04:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞄準
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.21,0:04:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.18,0:04:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.76,0:04:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,信號確認
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.99,0:04:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要開戰還是要撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.19,0:04:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請作選擇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.33,0:05:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能相信他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.23,0:05:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,司令，請下令開砲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.60,0:05:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,解除攻擊準備，撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.64,0:05:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,度西斯艦隊及其地上部隊\N開始撤退了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.42,0:05:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來對方司令官也瞭解\N騎士精神是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.95,0:05:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這世界還是有救的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.59,0:05:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您接下來可有得忙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.13,0:05:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.14,0:05:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光靠我們\N真的能把這裡全部修好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.94,0:05:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別多嘴，給我惦惦幹活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.35,0:05:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經連著三天徹夜工作\N幾乎都沒怎麼睡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.52,0:05:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再加上銀之戰艦\N現在就跟沒穿衣服一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.65,0:05:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣怎麼可能還去打仗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.75,0:06:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是怎麼啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.46,0:06:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫藍他在擔心生還章的運氣\N是不是終於給用完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.93,0:06:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們難道都不怕死嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.10,0:06:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.69,0:06:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.29,0:06:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.66,0:06:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.63,0:06:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.16,0:06:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.80,0:06:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們去找他好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.83,0:06:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是這個意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.07,0:06:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是說我搞不清楚\N克勞士他現在在想什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.90,0:06:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們吵架了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.84,0:06:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.67,0:06:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是我單方面說出了想說的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.68,0:06:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說我討厭現在的克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.95,0:06:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.75,0:07:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說出來後痛快多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.62,0:07:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我也想了很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.12,0:07:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過光是在那裡想也不是辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.72,0:07:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論是關於亞力克斯\N關於先鋒艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.86,0:07:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者是關於塔琪安娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.53,0:07:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些事情管它怎樣都好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.33,0:07:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正我喜歡先鋒艇就對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.27,0:07:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也希望能早一點讓克勞士\N回頭看看先鋒艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.98,0:07:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我決定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.52,0:07:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要退出嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.95,0:07:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是退出不坐先鋒艇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.62,0:07:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不知道發生了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.65,0:07:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那架先鋒艇\N是你父親的不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.86,0:07:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是亞力克斯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.99,0:07:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎麼樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.26,0:07:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你不要否定過去的自己好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.33,0:07:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我期待你能用那架先鋒艇\N飛越大風暴區
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.80,0:07:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是你的夢想嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.73,0:07:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳懂什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.54,0:07:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在的你\N感覺跟亞力克斯好像…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.44,0:07:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.51,0:08:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.35,0:08:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思，打擾你們正開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.46,0:08:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問艦長大人在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.69,0:08:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們是…送貨員嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.90,0:08:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.03,0:08:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,東西確實交給你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.77,0:08:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫我跟渥卡問好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.44,0:08:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會替你轉達的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.68,0:08:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你帶路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.64,0:08:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.61,0:08:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前進方向，地平洞窟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.12,0:08:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解，前進方向地平洞窟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.92,0:08:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.52,0:08:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們將停留地平洞窟幾天\N好作補給和修復
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.96,0:08:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳達給相關單位知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.60,0:08:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓他們進行準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.80,0:08:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.37,0:09:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.17,0:09:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你們兩位啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.47,0:09:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.21,0:09:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問你們送貨到銀之戰艦來\N都不會覺得害怕嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.28,0:09:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難免吧，畢竟是五顆星任務嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.52,0:09:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.95,0:09:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過人家我可是送貨的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.66,0:09:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要是工作所需\N無論是哪兒我都會送去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.26,0:09:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不瞞你說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.23,0:09:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好久沒做這個工作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.80,0:09:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為駕駛員不夠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.67,0:09:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們這些本來該退休的老人\N這下也有工作找上門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.21,0:09:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過話說回來\N天空這東西真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.47,0:09:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小夥子你也來飛飛看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.14,0:09:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺很讚哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.94,0:10:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以體會您的感受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.65,0:10:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對令尊的事情，我深感遺憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.52,0:10:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但陛下他已忘了天下蒼生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.69,0:10:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父王…已經是過去的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.80,0:10:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了和你討論今後的事情\N才來到這裡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.90,0:10:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼有一件事必須要去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.37,0:10:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,度西斯的司令官是個明理的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.01,0:10:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就以皇帝的身分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.77,0:10:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去見度西斯的司令官吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.44,0:10:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思，要你跑這一趟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.78,0:10:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於要動手了是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.02,0:11:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宰相吩咐要把關鍵謎詩交給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.89,0:11:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.09,0:11:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這天我等了好久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.40,0:11:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,記好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.06,0:11:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是達格貝家的關鍵謎詩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.47,0:11:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將大地染作金黃的波浪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.74,0:11:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將大地染作金黃的波浪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.61,0:11:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有一首\N宰相不是已經送來了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.28,0:11:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在還不到知道的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.05,0:11:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長\N已到達地平洞窟的領空了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.63,0:11:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本艦從現在開始\N即將進入地平洞窟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.37,0:11:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進行物資補給\N以及船身的修復作業
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.77,0:11:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前地平洞窟被開放為\N訓練奪取組件作戰用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.78,0:11:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安那托勒特殊部隊的訓練場地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.15,0:12:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已安排好大家可以自由使用\N他們的住宿設施
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.19,0:12:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請各自在出發前\N充分作好養精蓄銳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.52,0:12:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舉槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.99,0:12:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.86,0:12:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，下一排
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.13,0:12:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舉槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.53,0:12:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.21,0:12:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.52,0:12:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.67,0:12:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地平洞窟…那裡是幹什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.84,0:13:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是對總帥大人您不敬的\N一群下等人的根據地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.41,0:13:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.04,0:13:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些下等戰艦\N已開始集結在該洞窟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.08,0:13:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,表現出一些不甚安分的舉動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.15,0:13:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許他們正企圖破壞\N戴芬妮大人您的榮華…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.09,0:13:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,憑他們做得到嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.92,0:13:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人提議說\N要不要早點把組件收回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.46,0:13:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一來便能輕易阻止\N謀反的發生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.56,0:13:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.33,0:13:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用不知何時會消失的翅膀來飛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.94,0:13:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想必一定很有趣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.57,0:13:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果現在就把組件收回來\N就太沒意思了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.81,0:13:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要的就是那最精彩的一瞬間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.41,0:13:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這妳懂吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.02,0:13:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可悲的人們哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.89,0:13:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是…算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.52,0:13:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.89,0:13:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從沙漠回來以後\N妳變得很愛管閒事耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.29,0:13:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是希望你能在天上飛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.03,0:13:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.96,0:13:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以一名戰鬥機駕駛員的身分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.73,0:14:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你明明就不喜歡這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.57,0:14:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.77,0:14:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳這就叫多管閒事知道嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.67,0:14:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.74,0:14:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.34,0:14:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在拉薇她正在修先鋒艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.05,0:14:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也來嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.72,0:14:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…現在不方便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.35,0:14:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.05,0:14:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因…因為我在忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.29,0:14:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.96,0:14:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.76,0:14:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要去吃飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.00,0:14:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.23,0:14:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要和艾麗絲蒂亞去吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.43,0:14:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和大家一起去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.14,0:14:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼那小子\N會和小公主在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.14,0:14:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那當然是因為有過什麼\N所以關係匪淺囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.91,0:14:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算妳厲害，小公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.78,0:14:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那妳呢，要不要走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.42,0:14:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我解決完這個以後再去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.55,0:14:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們就這樣走掉不好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.59,0:14:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就體諒人家一下嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.12,0:14:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.99,0:15:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉，你怎麼那麼遲鈍\N走了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.10,0:15:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫藍到哪兒去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.81,0:15:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.64,0:15:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,槍兵不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.01,0:15:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨，你來了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.48,0:15:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這兒變得還真是通風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.25,0:15:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,採光又好，住起來挺舒服的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.82,0:15:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這都得感謝那位總帥大姊才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.69,0:15:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎喲，說到你的痛處了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.30,0:15:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,文生下手也太狠了一點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.43,0:15:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看我來把它修得跟新的一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.50,0:15:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有勞你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.80,0:15:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我聽說\N請款單是開給皇宮是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.31,0:15:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也滿不簡單的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.64,0:15:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，那東西終於弄好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.91,0:15:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.38,0:15:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是麻煩你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.69,0:16:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.66,0:16:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不和葛溫他們一起去吃飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.36,0:16:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼我都想來這裡看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.46,0:16:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的是很喜歡先鋒艇呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.90,0:16:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.93,0:16:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是在苦惱什麼事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.64,0:16:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我哪有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.14,0:16:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.84,0:16:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看得出來，你的表情怪怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.04,0:16:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,表情？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.04,0:16:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很怪嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.41,0:16:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怪到不行\N根本不像平常的克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.78,0:16:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.09,0:16:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.59,0:16:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.09,0:16:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們在幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.33,0:16:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉爾夫！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.06,0:16:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…你是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.93,0:16:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姬塔在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.74,0:16:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.80,0:16:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你和我們認識的一個人\N長得實在太像了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.21,0:16:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，那個機首像…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.68,0:16:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是一位叫做\N拉爾夫‧溫斯地的駕駛員給我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.78,0:17:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要吃嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.76,0:17:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有一根哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.29,0:17:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.83,0:17:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉爾夫是我弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.30,0:17:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能接下我的任務…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.97,0:17:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.78,0:17:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先鋒艇駕駛員和先鋒艇一起\N被炸得連影子都不剩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.11,0:17:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他這也算是求仁得仁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.12,0:17:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要代我弟弟謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.72,0:17:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你幫他完成了他的任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.82,0:17:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我當時沒有想太多…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.93,0:17:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個就給你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.73,0:17:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.10,0:17:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望由你來保有它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.37,0:17:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由你這位先鋒艇駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.77,0:18:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來在不知情裡\N我也算是在為弟弟報仇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.61,0:18:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說這是特殊部隊\N到底都是在做什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.05,0:18:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在演習
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.48,0:18:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以安那托勒的宰相\N當初逃出基爾特時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.99,0:18:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所搭乘的戰艦為攻擊練習目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.46,0:18:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟以先鋒艇去攻擊戰艦\N怎麼說都是空前之舉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.56,0:18:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安那托勒的先鋒艇駕駛員\N幾乎都被網羅來此了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.47,0:18:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不也是為此而來的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.77,0:18:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.51,0:18:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.88,0:18:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,旋風霍克！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.38,0:18:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胖胖雞！陽光男孩！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.12,0:18:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,旋風霍克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.79,0:18:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.89,0:18:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,旋風霍克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.43,0:18:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來你還活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.73,0:18:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時我還以為你一定沒救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.03,0:18:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還好你也沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.60,0:19:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說諾齊亞被度西斯佔領了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.10,0:19:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是不可能會為了這點小事\N而放棄飛行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.51,0:19:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.18,0:19:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，賴床寶寶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.81,0:19:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是克勞士嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.41,0:19:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胖胖雞，陽光男孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.98,0:19:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…感覺好像少了些什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.08,0:19:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是叫我鼻毛小子吧\N那樣才像你嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.99,0:19:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會那樣叫你的是拉薇啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.42,0:19:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，拉薇她怎樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.33,0:19:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.56,0:19:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去叫她來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.36,0:19:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子是誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.40,0:19:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…說來話長…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.03,0:19:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你幹嘛吞吞吐吐的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.17,0:19:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還想把這個秀給你瞧瞧的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.11,0:19:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是諾齊亞盃的冠軍獎章嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.08,0:19:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊，嚇到了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.41,0:19:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這還不是因為當時\N我和克勞士退出了比賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.85,0:19:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這根本就是狗屎運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.22,0:19:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少囉唆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.48,0:19:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨便你們怎麼說啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.09,0:19:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正是本大爺贏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.09,0:19:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙很討人厭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.99,0:19:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從那以後他一直就這德性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.59,0:20:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天哪，鼻毛小子，大肥雞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.39,0:20:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.73,0:20:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還好吧，旋風霍克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.20,0:20:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.47,0:20:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是少了這個\N怎麼能叫做和你們重逢呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.34,0:20:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.24,0:20:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們知道嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.74,0:20:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的贊助者\N可是諾齊亞的麥德賽侯爵哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.85,0:20:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麥德賽！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.22,0:20:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊\N諾齊亞的人都嚇了一大跳呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.95,0:20:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根據麥德賽侯爵的說法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.65,0:20:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新時代的戰爭\N將要靠先鋒艇來主導
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.82,0:20:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,據說是在米納紀斯會戰裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.46,0:20:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一架送貨的先鋒艇\N在戰場上大出風頭的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.80,0:20:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎就是當時的那件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.20,0:20:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為這次攻擊基爾特的行動\N帶來了不少啟示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.43,0:20:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時的送貨員\N該不會就是你們吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.15,0:20:53.11,OD,,0000,0000,0000,,我問你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.31,0:20:55.84,OD,,0000,0000,0000,,你有沒有因為肚子餓得\N而睡不著覺過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.92,0:20:57.65,OD,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼騎士精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.82,0:20:59.15,OD,,0000,0000,0000,,全是放屁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.22,0:21:01.21,OD,,0000,0000,0000,,去做我們能做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.30,0:21:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能是他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.24,0:21:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,諾齊亞的天空\N可是我們的地盤呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.21,0:21:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士，拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.38,0:21:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼送貨的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.65,0:21:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼新的戰爭…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.82,0:21:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們只不過是\N拼命把工作做好而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.15,0:21:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虧我們還那麼抗拒\N先鋒艇被當成戰爭的道具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.99,0:21:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們…難不成…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.43,0:21:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時我只認為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.83,0:21:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是先鋒艇的話\N應該可以做些什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.83,0:21:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯\N只有先鋒艇能做到的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.07,0:21:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到卻把大家\N捲入了戰爭的天空下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.54,0:21:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.81,0:21:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是克勞士你一個人的責任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.78,0:21:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.41,0:22:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我把大家…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.55,0:22:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.19,0:22:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我絕不能再逃避這片天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.49,0:22:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不能再逃避先鋒艇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.49,0:22:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.18,0:22:39.28,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,黑夜的時光逐漸逼近\N{\c&HFFBF00&}夜の時間が迫り来る
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.02,0:22:45.69,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你離我如此接近感覺  卻好遠…\N{\c&HFFBF00&}あなたはこんな近く でも遠い…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.76,0:22:51.32,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你的憧憬是什麼\N{\c&HFFBF00&}何に憧れて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.40,0:22:57.03,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,心中想的又是誰\N{\c&HFFBF00&}だれを想うのか
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.10,0:23:02.80,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你奮不顧身的身影\N{\c&HFFBF00&}いのち賭ける姿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.88,0:23:11.72,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,有一種透明的美麗  令我噤聲無言\N{\c&HFFBF00&}透き通る美しさに 言葉を飲んだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.79,0:23:17.69,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你欲飛往天際\N{\c&HFFBF00&}あなたが空を行くなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.76,0:23:23.32,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,我願成為你的翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}わたしは翼になりたい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.40,0:23:29.20,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,無論風有多麼強\N{\c&HFFBF00&}どんなに強い風にも
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.27,0:23:35.07,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,也永遠不會折斷的柔婉翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}けして折れない しなやかな羽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.14,0:23:47.52,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,相信有一天  我會擁有那樣一對翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}いつか　きっと持つから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.23,0:23:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(下回預告)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.93,0:23:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗚…英麥曼他討厭我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.00,0:23:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會這樣，魯修拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.93,0:23:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.87,0:24:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許是剛才那段話\N說的不得體吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.13,0:24:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.77,0:24:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是覺得滿好記又好聽呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.58,0:24:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一回，最後流亡 第18話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.58,0:24:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘇菲亞升級\NPromotion Sophia
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.48,0:24:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你與我是兩顆流星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.08,0:24:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起變成流星吧，英麥曼
